{{unsourced|date=January 2014}} {{Infobox summit | summit_name = Arab League summit | other_titles = | image = | caption = | country = [[Egypt]] | venues = | cities = [[Cairo]] | date = {{Start date|1976|10|25}} | website = }}
The '''1976 Arab League summit''' was held on October 25 in [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]] less than two weeks after the [[1976 Arab League summit (Riyadh)|Riyadh summit]]. The summit had a wider Arab participation and was dedicated to following up on the deteriorating situation in [[Lebanon]]. The outcome of the summit was the formation and deployment of an Arab peacekeeping force in Lebanon.
