'''VeggieWorld''' are annual [[Veganism|vegan]] [[food]] [[festival]]s held in numerous locations around Europe.<ref>{{cite web|title=Veggie World by VEBU|url=https://vebu.de/veranstaltungen/veggie-world|accessdate=31 August 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=VeggieWorld|url=http://veggieworld.de/en/dfaskdjfalksdfj-2|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220161833/http://veggieworld.de/en/dfaskdjfalksdfj-2|dead-url=yes|archive-date=20 February 2016|accessdate=31 August 2015|df=dmy-all}}</ref>
These festivals take place in the following countries: cities: * [[Germany]]: [[Düsseldorf]], [[Berlin]], [[Frankfurt Rhine-Main|Rhein-Main]], [[Hamburg]], [[Munich]] * [[France]]: [[Paris]] * [[Netherlands]]: [[Utrecht]] (since 2016)<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://nos.nl/op3/artikel/2090859-gaat-het-nieuwe-vlees-het-oude-vlees-verslaan.html |title=Gaat het nieuwe vlees het oude vlees verslaan? |work=NOS |date=5 March 2016 |accessdate=26 March 2017 |language=nl}}</ref> * [[Switzerland]]: [[Zurich]]
